# Sample audio: publish only the curated, attributed files. Recordings added
# through the playground's "Add from device" land in this folder and must not
# be committed (they are unattributed and may exceed the upload limit).
/samples-audio/*
!/samples-audio/ATTRIBUTION.md
!/samples-audio/harvard.wav
!/samples-audio/jackhammer.wav
